  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360710/extras/ac1d3723f32b6eda46e06a2e490a5c14.avif?t=1695315858\" width=640 height=350 /></span><br><br>Survive in a hostile space environment with randomized damage, drop and enemy strength. Adjust difficulty yourself dynamically with upgrading weapons, but be careful not always the upgrade succeeds.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360710/extras/297e813bc1a98979e03d5ab928f73b67.avif?t=1695315858\" width=640 height=350 /></span><br><br>Players can use Weapons to fight their way through space in hostile environment of space ship. Not only Dual Wielding of weapons but also a upgrades are possible. Players can upgrade weapons with components that drop from enemies or use these components for advancing in story. Weapons and projectiles can lead to dismemberment.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360710/extras/4b992e38bbdfb27df6956cc37d6e7c5b.avif?t=1695315858\" width=640 height=350 /></span>",
